We will be using the R programming language to do our statistics. 

Start by installing R:
https://mirrors.dotsrc.org/cran/

The, install Rstudio. R studio is the editor we use to write and run R-code in.
https://rstudio.com/products/rstudio/download/#download

Finally, do a couple of simple R-exercises to get the basics down.
https://www.datacamp.com/courses/free-introduction-to-r
